#Map settings
N_cities 34                              #Number of cities 
Cities_on_circle 1                       #1 cities on circumference, 0 cities in square
#Population settings 
Pop_size 200                            #Population size 
N_gen 500                              #Number of generations
#Genetic algorithm parameters
P_m 0.1                                 #Mutation probability
P_x 0.8                                #Crossover probability
sel_p 5.0                               #exponent for individuals selection
#Mutation shares: must be S_W+S_R+S_P+S_S=1
S_W 0.05                                 # Share of swap mutation
S_R 0.5                                # Share of reverse mutation 
S_P 0.05                               # Share of permutate mutation
S_S 0.4                               # Share of shift mutation 


END